<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8" />
  <style type="text/css">
    body {
      font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      background-color: #f4f4f4;
      color: #333333;
    }
    .container {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    }
    .header {
      text-align: center;
      padding-bottom: 20px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #dddddd;
    }
    .header img {
      max-width: 150px; /* 您可以替換成您的 AI ENGLISH Logo URL */
    }
    .content {
      padding: 20px 0;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    .content h1 {
      font-size: 22px;
      color: #333333;
    }
    .content p {
      font-size: 16px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .button-container {
      text-align: center;
      margin: 30px 0;
    }
    .button {
      background-color: #007bff; /* 一個專業的藍色 */
      color: #ffffff;
      padding: 15px 30px;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 5px;
      font-size: 16px;
      font-weight: bold;
      display: inline-block;
    }
    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      padding-top: 20px;
      border-top: 1px solid #dddddd;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #777777;
    }
    .footer a {
      color: #007bff;
      text-decoration: none;
    }
    .small-text {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #777777;
      margin-top: 15px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <%# 替換為您的 Logo 圖片路徑或 URL %>
      <%# link_to image_tag('your_logo.png', alt: 'AI ENGLISH Logo'), root_url %>
      <%# 如果沒有現成 Logo，可以先用文字 %>
      <h2>AI ENGLISH</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <h1>Confirm Your Recovery Email Address</h1>
      <p>Hi <%= @user.nickname || @user.email %>,</p>
      <p>
        You recently added or updated this email address (<%= @user.recovery_email %>) as a recovery email for your AI ENGLISH account.
      </p>
      <p>
        To complete this process and ensure this email address can be used for account recovery in the future, please click the button below to confirm its validity.
      </p>
      <div class="button-container">
        <a href="<%= @confirmation_url %>" class="button">Confirm Recovery Email</a>
      </div>
      <p>
        If you did not request this change, or if you believe this was an error, please ignore this email. No changes will be made to your account unless you confirm.
      </p>
      <p>
        This confirmation link is valid for a limited time. If the link has expired, please try adding or updating your recovery email again through your AI ENGLISH account settings.
      </p>
      <p>Thank you,<br>The AI ENGLISH Team</p>
      <p class="small-text">
        If you're having trouble clicking the button, copy and paste the URL below into your web browser:<br>
        <a href="<%= @confirmation_url %>"><%= @confirmation_url %></a>
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>&copy; <%= Time.now.year %> AI ENGLISH. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
